title: Anthony Albanese - Wikipedia
snippet: Albanese pledged his first act in his second term would be to reduce tertiary education loans by 20%. Legislation to put this reduction into effect passed on 31 July 2025.

title: Anthony Albanese - Kids | Britannica Kids | Homework Help
snippet: Albanese was the first person in his family to finish high school, and he continued his studies at the University of Sydney. He worked multiple jobs while in school. Albanese graduated with a degree in economics in 1984.

title: Anthony Albanese - Anthony's Story
snippet: After juggling multiple jobs while studying full time, he graduated from the University of Sydney with a Bachelor of Economics. Anthony knows the impact that a good education can have on your life.
